'''''Star Wars Insider'' 69''' is the sixty-ninth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands in [[July]] [[2003]]. The subscriber-exclusive edition of issue 69 included the fourth volume of ''[[Bantha Tracks (department)|Bantha Tracks]]'', the [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Official ''Star Wars'' Fan Club]] newsletter.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk"
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Star News]]"
*"[[HoloNet News (Insider)|HoloNet News]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
**"[[Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 14:9:01]]"
**"[[CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:9:08 Edition]]"
*"[[Behind the Magic]]" &mdash; Separatists at Birth {{C|by [[Rob Coleman]]}}
*"[[Toy Box]]" &mdash; The Fans' Choice {{C|by Andy@Hasbro}}
*"[[Gamescape]]"
